        {
            "id": 6011259,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 美卡多(MELI-US)大跌5.08%，報2450.48美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美卡多(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MELI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MELI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MELI-US</a>)截至台北時間06日21:33股價下跌131.26美元，報2450.48美元，跌幅5.08%，成交量39,507（股），盤中最高價2545.95美元、最低價2450.48美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+1.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.75%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>美卡多(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MELI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MELI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MELI-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.42%</li> <li>近 1 月：+14.92%</li> <li>近 3 月：+22.2%</li> <li>近 6 月：+30.07%</li> <li>今年以來：+51.83%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6011259",
